tourBios.carHigh:
Made three cuts in 2012, with a season- best finish of T-27 at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open

Made 2 of 11 cuts in 2011 with his best finish coming at the Dakota Dunes Casino Open, Received non-exempt status for 2011 after finishing T-17 at the 2010 Fall Qualifying School, Finished the 2010 season with a T-43 at the Desert Dunes Classic, Finished T-10 at the 2009 Desjardins Montreal Open, Lost his card in 2008 but regained non-exempt status in 2009 with rounds of 66-71-71- 75 at the Florida Winter Qualifying School, Acquired non-exempt status at the 2008 Florida Winter Qualifying School.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Latinoameri was T27th in 2013 at the Personal Classic presented by BlackBerry.
